                            <comment id="16141749" author="garydgregory" created="Fri, 25 Aug 2017 15:15:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;May you please post the NPE?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16141765" author="einmalfel" created="Fri, 25 Aug 2017 15:30:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, should have attach it initially:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.NullPointerException:&lt;br/&gt;
at org.apache.commons.net.telnet.TelnetClient._flushOutputStream (Unknown Source)&lt;br/&gt;
at org.apache.commons.net.telnet.TelnetOutputStream.flush (Unknown Source)&lt;br/&gt;
at java.io.PrintStream.flush (PrintStream.java:257)&lt;br/&gt;
at java.io.PrintStream.close (PrintStream.java:237)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16356844" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Thu, 8 Feb 2018 11:50:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like the stream has been closed (or has not yet been opened).&lt;br/&gt;
It should not give NPE, instead it should raise IOException(&quot;Stream closed&quot;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, close() should be idempotent.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
